text: Boulevard Nights is a 1979 American crime movie directed by Michael Pressman and starring Richard Yniguez, Danny De La Paz, Carmen Zapata, Victor Millan, James Victor, Daniel Zacapa. It was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * Category:1979 crime movies Category:American crime movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Pressman
